name: CASIO-MINI Electronic Calculator CM-602 (1973)
description:
"CASIO-MINI Electronic Calculator CM-602" 1973 handheld electronic calculator X-ray image. Radiated by Iñigo Bilbao. 2021. 2500x2500p. JPG.
Modified version of Casio’s first commercial handheld electronic calculator, the CASIO-MINI CM-601 (August 1972).
A June 1973 advertisement in the Los Angeles Times shows the CASIO-MINI CM-602 as on sale for $59.95.
